snippet.title: Selena Gomez And Andy Samberg Come Back For 'Hotel Transylvania: Transformania'
snippet.description:
"Hotel Transylvania" gears up for its fourth installment with stars Selena Gomez and Andy Samberg reprising their respective roles. Gomez describes her favourite part of the film and her joy returning to play Mavis.
